906
00:38:26,960 --> 00:38:27,920
Did they find her?

907
00:38:57,400 --> 00:38:58,239
Captain, she is awake.

908
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,519
Go get the doctor.

909
00:39:00,159 --> 00:39:00,559
Okay.

910
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:03,320
Don't move!

911
00:39:11,599 --> 00:39:12,159
Li Jin,

912
00:39:13,519 --> 00:39:14,039
it's not

913
00:39:14,519 --> 00:39:15,760
that easy to die.

914
00:39:16,559 --> 00:39:17,679
Think about it carefully.

915
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,079
The suspect

916
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:29,320
cut her own wind pipe

917
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,000
and vocal cords.

918
00:39:30,159 --> 00:39:31,000
The wound's been treated.

919
00:39:31,119 --> 00:39:32,199
But she can't speak yet.

920
00:39:32,679 --> 00:39:33,239
Her emotions

921
