930
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:09,400
Thank you.

931
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:10,199
I'll go back

932
00:40:10,199 --> 00:40:11,280
and start the transfer paperwork.

933
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:13,960
This case doesn't seem complicated.

934
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:15,199
It's just that

935
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:17,079
