953
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:55,760
If she cooperates now,

954
00:40:56,039 --> 00:40:56,840
it would certainly

955
00:40:56,880 --> 00:40:57,880
be considered in sentencing.

956
00:40:59,000 --> 00:40:59,840
But she's totally

957
