I thought I was done for.

973
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:31,159
But when I opened my eyes,

974
00:42:32,239 --> 00:42:33,239
I saw your face.

975
00:42:34,400 --> 00:42:35,719
You protected me under your body,

976
00:42:36,559 --> 00:42:37,199
