983
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:53,320
Don't be afraid.

984
00:42:54,519 --> 00:42:55,079
Don't be afraid."

985
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,280
I can never forget

986
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:01,079
